# portfoliomanager

Portfolio Manager allows HR firms to manage their candidate list.

## Candidates Collection [/api/candidates]

### List All Candidates [GET]

You may view a list of candidates using this action.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "candidates": [
                {
                    "@context": {
                        "birthday": "http://schema.org/birthDate",
