### Create a New Candidate [POST]

You may create a new candidate using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a candidate's attributes.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "first_name": "John",
            "last_name": "Doe",
            "email": "john@doe.com",
            "birthday":"1989-01-21",
            "phone": "123-567-123"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "id": 17,
                "url": "/api/candidates/17"
            }


